New Avengers v1 (001 - 064 + Extras) (2005 - 2010) (digital) (Minutemen-PhD) 


New Avengers Volume 1

The series is a revamp of the Avengers vol.3 series. After the events of Avengers Disassembled, a new group of Avengers was created from the ashes. But the Civil War changed the heroes forever, not only with the death of Captain America but changing the status of the New Avengers as fugitives of the law. The roster included Wolverine, Spider-Man, Ronin, Echo, Dr. Strange, Iron Fist, Bucky as Captain America and their leader, Luke Cage.
